node.text: Tag your beer buddies!🍻🥨 Get ready to prost at NYC's biggest indoor/outdoor Oktoberfest. With a live performance by @NOTD, epic beer garden & more! Tickets now available at Bucketlisters.com or link-in-bio @NYBucketlist 🎟️
